Reference manual:
http://opencv.willowgarage.com/documentation/cpp/index.html

Setting up OpenCV on Mac OS X
=============================
* Download OpenCV 2.1
   http://sourceforge.net/projects/opencvlibrary/files/opencv-unix/2.1/OpenCV-2.1.0.tar.bz2/download
* Decompress to
   cinder/blocks/opencv/ as OpenCV, resulting in
      cinder/blocks/opencv/OpenCV
* cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=RELEASE -D BUILD_PYTHON_SUPPORT=OFF -D BUILD_NEW_PYTHON_SUPPORT=OFF -D BUILD_EXAMPLES=OFF -D BUILD_TESTS=OFF -D BUILD_SHARED_LIBS=OFF -D CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS="-mmacosx-version-min=10.5" -D CMAKE_OSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET=10.5 -D CMAKE_OSX_SYSROOT=/Developer/SDKs/MacOSX10.5.sdk -D CMAKE_OSX_ARCHITECTURES="i386;x86_64" -D OPENCV_EXTRA_C_FLAGS="-mmacosx-version-min=10.5" .
* make -j 8



Creating a Project on Mac OS X
==============================
* Using TinderBox, create a new app based on BasicApp
* Under Project Settings, All Configurations
   Header Search Paths += $(CINDER_PATH)/blocks/opencv/OpenCV
   User Header Search Paths += ../../../include